Class TournamentFragment

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class TournamentFragment
extends android.support.v4.app.Fragment
implements android.view.View.OnClickListener
    TournamentFragment inflates layout defined in fragment_layout.xml This fragment holds the first fragment layout in the view pager. Tournaments can be loaded and created from this fragment.
